                            </l>
                        </texthead>
                        <vspace extent="1"/>
                        <lg type="verse" justify="left">
                            <l n="bb444.1.1.com.01.05" justify="left">And when the storms of life are past</l>
                            <l n="bb444.1.1.com.01.06" justify="left"> Hope drops her anchor here at last</l>
                        </lg>
